        "subject": "LU-0000 build: update build version to 2.5.3.90",
        "message": "LU-0000 build: update build version to 2.5.3.90\n\nThe current b2_5 has diverged significantly from 2.5.3.0 but it still\nhas the same version number in the builds, which is confusing.\n\nThere may also be problems in the build system for using patch version\nnumbers, which should be found by this patch.\n\nUpdate the build version to 2.5.3.90.\n\nSigned-off-by: Andreas Dilger <andreas.dilger@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I814c3d693ae4dbb4ae9975f90fcc531752300c1e\nReviewed-on: http://review.whamcloud.com/13815\nTested-by: Jenkins\nTested-by: Maloo <hpdd-maloo@intel.com>\nReviewed-by: Oleg Drokin <oleg.drokin@intel.com>\n"
      },
